    "ThreadId": "64027",
    "Html": "<p>I have scrollviewer at my Window/UserControl is set to Auto. &nbsp;My screen has three sections. &nbsp;the &quot;top&quot; section and &quot;bottom&quot; section are static in height when expanded. &nbsp;I want my data grid to be able to grow to fix the whitespace. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I also want to set a maxheight (dynamically?) so that the data grid itself will not grow past the whitespace &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The the datagrid scrollbars will never appear unless I set the max height. &nbsp;The challenge is that my data grid is dynamic and the rest of my screen is not.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>How can I set the datagrid's maxheight dynamically?</p>\r\n<p>Here is the Psuedocode:</p>\r\n<p>&lt;ScrollViewer&gt;</p>\r\n<div style=\"color:Black;background-color:White\">\r\n<pre><span style=\"color:Blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">Grid</span> <span style=\"color:Red\">x:Name</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">gridCenterMain</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">DockPanel</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t</span>&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">StackPanel</span> <span style=\"color:Red\">DockPanel.Dock</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">Top</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t</span>&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">Expander</span> <span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t</span>&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">Canvas</span> <span style=\"color:Red\">Height</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">85</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;  &lt;&lt;--STATIC HEIGHT</span>\r\n\t\t<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t</span>//Filter controls\r\n<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t</span>&lt;/Canvas\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t</span>&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">Expander</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t</span>&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">Expander</span> <span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t</span>&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">Canvas</span>  <span style=\"color:Red\">Height</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">Auto</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n\t\t<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">DataGrid</span> <span style=\"color:Red\">Canvas.Left</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">24</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:Red\">Canvas.Top</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">12</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">/&gt;  &lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;----THIS NEEDS TO HAVE MAX HEIGHT SET DYNAMICALLY SO SCROLLBARS APPEAR</span>\r\n<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t</span>&lt;/Canvas\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t</span>&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">Expander</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t</span>&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span></pre>\r\n<pre><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t</span>&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">Canvas</span>  <span style=\"color:Red\">DockPanel.Dock</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">Bottom</span><span style=\"color:Black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t</span>//bottom buttons      <span style=\"color:#0000ff\">&lt;&lt;--STATIC HEIGHT</span><br>\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t</span>&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">Canvas</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">DockPanel</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:Blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">Grid</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n&lt;/ScrollViewer&gt;</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Regards,</p>\r\n<p>Tracy</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
